English:
--------
Year: 2012
Version: v1.1
Platform: x64/86
Compatible with Windows 7 full time
Language: Multilingual
License: Freeware
Size: 931 Mb


Set the minimum required software, which is always with you. The updated version consists of free or "open" programs.

New in v1.1:
1. Programme updated to the latest versions of relevant
2. The set takes up less space (removed the program requiring "treatment")
3. Pirated copies of software are replaced by free analogues
4. The set is placed on a carrier with 1GB of memory
5. Added a convenient and logical menu

installation:
1. Run the USB-Set v1.1.exe
2. Specify the path to your USB-flash drive
3. Click to extract
4. Wait for the installation

Attention!
For comfort and neat appearance, directory of programs and system files are hidden. If you want to display all the files - uncheck the attribute "hidden" in your important files.

System requirements:
Windows XP \ Vista \ 7
USB-drive with 1GB of memory
